name:                esqueleto
version:             1.3.7
synopsis:            Bare bones, type-safe EDSL for SQL queries on persistent backends.
homepage:            https://github.com/meteficha/esqueleto
license:             BSD3
license-file:        LICENSE
author:              Felipe Lessa
